Package: metahelpers
Type: Package
Title: Convenience Wrappers for Three-Level Random-Effects Meta-Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Mohamadjavad", "Ershadmanesh", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "dr.mjershad@gmail.com")
Description: A small set of convenience wrappers over 'metafor' and
    'clubSandwich' for the common pattern of effect sizes nested within
    clusters. Provides fit_three_level() to set up the two random-effects
    strata and attach CR2 cluster-robust standard errors, multilevel I^2
    decomposition, prediction intervals, and a broom-style tidier.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    stats
Suggests:
    metafor,
    clubSandwich,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
